    public final class ResourceQuotaOptionsV1Update
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure
    The ResourceQuotaOptionsV1Update class represents the changes to resource quota limits which are set on the namespace. Refer to <\a> Kubernetes Resource Quota for information related to the properties of this object and what they map to.
